{
  "id": "adv_card_rui_09_02",
  "title": "天動瑠依 2話 大事に着ますね",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshimifes-03-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshimifes-03-night",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshimifes-03-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshimifes-03-night",
      "startTime": 6.5333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_02-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "シェアなんてしたら、そんなの……か、か、間接……\nダ、ダメです！　そんな気軽に、絶対ダメですっ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If we share‚ that would be… i-i-indirect…\nN-no good! So casually‚ absolutely not!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshimifes-03-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshimifes-03-night",
      "startTime": 11.5333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "そんなにダメか？　どこかで箸と皿を余分にもらえば\n取り分けたりしてシェア出来ると思ったんだけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is it that bad? If we get extra chopsticks and plates somewhere‚\nI thought we could portion it out and share.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshimifes-03-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshimifes-03-night",
      "startTime": 19.8333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_02-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "お箸とお皿を……あっ、そうですよね！　それなら\n問題なくシェア出来ますね！　そうしましょう！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Chopsticks and plates… oh‚ that's right! In that case\nwe can share without any problems! Let's do that!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshimifes-03-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshimifes-03-night",
      "startTime": 29.1666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "そんな勢いよく言うほど楽しみなのか……？\nまぁ色々食べてみたいしな。それじゃあ、買いに行こう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Are you that excited to say it so enthusiastically…?\nWell‚ I want to try various things too. Then let's go buy them.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshimifes-03-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshimifes-03-night",
      "startTime": 37.6333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_02-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "一杯買っちゃいましたね\nあ……。あれ、可愛い……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We bought so much.\nOh… That's cute…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "瑠依？　どうかしたのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rui? What's wrong?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.866666158,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshimifes-03-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshimifes-03-night",
      "startTime": 47.2333346049
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_02-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "あ！　いえ、なんでもありません\n少しぼーっとしちゃってました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh! No‚ it's nothing.\nI was spacing out a little.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.8666684468,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "大丈夫か？　さすがに人も多いしな\n早く楽屋に戻って、買ったものを食べようか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Are you okay? There really are a lot of people.\nLet's hurry back to the dressing room and eat what we bought.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.0666684468,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshimifes-03-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshimifes-03-night",
      "startTime": 59.7666679382
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "（でも、さっき瑠依が見てたのって）\n（浴衣を着た女の子達だったような……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（But what Rui was looking at earlier）\n（seemed to be girls wearing yukata…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.0000017802,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshimifes-03-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshimifes-03-night",
      "startTime": 66.8666679382
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "（瑠依だって年頃の女の子だ。浴衣で着飾って）\n（友達とお祭りを楽しみたいのかもしれないな）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Rui is also a girl of that age. She probably wants）\n（to dress up in yukata and enjoy festivals with friends.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.7333351135,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 75.1166679382
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 75.1166679382
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_02-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "ごちそうさまでした\nわたあめも焼きそばも、とっても美味しかったです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you for the meal.\nBoth the cotton candy and yakisoba were really delicious.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.0666684468,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_02-rui006.m4a",
      "text": "食べなれた味でも、お祭りで買ったと思うと\n普段より美味しく感じますね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even familiar flavors‚ when you think you bought them at a festival\nthey taste better than usual.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.3375661168,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 87.7666669209
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_02-rui007.m4a",
      "text": "あ、これMCに使えるかも。他にもヨーヨーすくいを\nした話とか……屋台の種類が沢山あった話も……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ I might be able to use this for MC. Also the story about yo-yo fishing…\nand the story about there being many types of stalls…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.4588052611,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 97.2666669209
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "お祭りで、見たり食べたり、感じたことを話題に……か\nお客さんも、親近感がわいていいと思うぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Using what you saw‚ ate‚ and felt at the festival as topics… I see.\nI think the audience will feel a sense of familiarity too‚ which is good.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.9000007629,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 106.0000038147
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_02-rui008.m4a",
      "text": "はい。折角みんなと同じお祭りを楽しめましたから！\n……うん、いい感じにまとめられそうです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes. Since I was able to enjoy the same festival as everyone!\n…Yeah‚ I think I can put it together well.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110.9333376567,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "よし、そろそろステージの時間だ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Alright‚ it's almost time for the stage",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.2000038147,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 117.2666704814
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_02-rui009.m4a",
      "text": "……あ、もうこんなに時間が経っていたんですね\n気づきませんでした",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Oh‚ so much time has already passed.\nI didn't notice.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.1315564178,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 122.9000038147
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_02-rui010.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん\n一緒に回ってくれて、ありがとうございました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san\nThank you for going around with me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.4333376567,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_02-rui011.m4a",
      "text": "お祭りを楽しませてもらった分も\n集まってくれたみなさんを、楽しませてきますね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "As much as I enjoyed the festival‚\nI'll make sure to entertain everyone who came!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.3333376567,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4899.999491300008,
          "startTime": 135.233337148
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_feststage-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "feststage-00-night",
      "startTime": 134.983337148
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_feststage-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "feststage-00-night",
      "startTime": 135.233337148
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_02-rui012.m4a",
      "text": "ここまで聴いてくれてありがとうございます。こんなに\n素敵なステージに立たせてもらえて、本当に嬉しいです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you for listening this far. I'm really happy\nto be able to stand on such a wonderful stage.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 139.7336545308,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_02-rui013.m4a",
      "text": "実は私も、少し前にお祭りを見て回っていたんですよ\nふふっ、誰にも気づかれませんでしたけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Actually‚ I was also looking around the festival a little while ago.\nFufu‚ nobody noticed though.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 149.3333376567,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 11466.662343300015,
          "startTime": 160.8
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_feststage-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "feststage-00-night",
      "startTime": 152.7000038147
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_02-rui014.m4a",
      "text": "焼きそばやお好み焼き、それからわたあめ\nどれも美味しかったです。みなさんは何を食べました？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yakisoba‚ okonomiyaki‚ and cotton candy\nthey were all delicious. What did everyone eat?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 156.8333376567,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_feststage-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "feststage-00-night",
      "startTime": 161.7000038147
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
